{"tid":2212048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★施麗珊：$10000 來得太遲 不少新移民「捱咗好多個月」！","createTime":"2020-09-21T13:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T13:03:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5c78b99c7795e58daa3d49b80b53612b5c43f9db","tid":2212048,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"政府關愛基金今日（21日）公布「低收入家庭的新來港定居成員一次過津貼」計劃詳情，將向低收入家庭的新來港定居成員發放一次過津貼，每人可申領一萬元。<br />\n<br />\n香港社區組織協會幹事施麗珊稱，不少新移民任職前線服務性行業，疫情下最需要支援，直言支援太遲，他們「捱咗好多個月」。她質疑政府為怕惹批評而遲遲未推出計劃，但認為抗疫為全港的目標。她又批評申請手續繁複，當中要求申請者上載證明文件，惟基層家庭未必有掃描器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/526464/%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B37%E5%B9%B4%E8%80%85%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%80%E8%90%AC-%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%A7%E8%A6%81%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%8A%A9%E5%A2%9E%E5%80%BC-%E7%AD%89%E6%95%91%E5%91%BD%E5%B0%B1%E6%AD%BB%E5%92%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F526464%2F%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B37%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%2580%25BC-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2592%2597&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEW%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=54692b7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/526464/%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B37%E5%B9%B4%E8%80%85%E7%8D%B2%E4%B8%80%E8%90%AC-%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%A7%E8%A6%81%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%8A%A9%E5%A2%9E%E5%80%BC-%E7%AD%89%E6%95%91%E5%91%BD%E5%B0%B1%E6%AD%BB%E5%92%97</a>"},{"pid":"95c16851fe4a542f2f0cabb57f6614979e20c089","tid":2212048,"uid":19454,"like":